  "name": "Agoria",
  "profile": "Influenced by jazz and Detroit techno, Sébastien Devaud aka Agoria is one in a long line of artists to emerge from the French electronic scene.\r\n\r\nIn 2000, he was the first DJ to be taken on by the prestigious FAIR, a French support fund for new acts, signing his first publishing contract with Peer Music the same year.\r\n\r\nHe left [l76448]'s A&R in 2011 and founded [l1060091] in 2016.\r\n",
